# Scope Discipline

Each prompt should introduce only one new concept.

Prefer extending the current architecture over replacing it.

Do not rewrite working code unless explicitly asked.

Avoid generating large files.

If a component grows beyond a few hundred lines or has multiple responsibilities, recommend splitting it into smaller components.

Favor composition over inheritance.

## Before implementing

Ask:

- Can this be built from existing components?
- Can this become a reusable component?
- Should this be data instead of code?
